    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies proactive, in-band network layer OAM mechanisms to detect loss of continuity faults that affect unicast and multi-destination paths (used by Broadcast, Unknown Unicast, and Multicast traffic) in an Ethernet VPN (RFC 7432bis) network. The mechanisms specified in the draft use the widely adopted Bidirectional Forwarding Detection (RFC 5880) protocol and other protocols as necessary.</t>
